= finalize

Finalizerとは, あるオブジェクト obj がGCされる時に obj に依存しているオブジェクトに対
してメッセージを送る機能です.

== 使いかた

  require 'finalize'

((<執筆者募集>))

((<ruby-list:3465>))

== モジュール関数

--- Finalizer.add(obj, dependant, method = :finalize, *opt)
--- Finalizer.add_dependency(obj, dependant, method = :finalize, *opt)

--- Finalizer.delete(id, dependant, method = :finalize)
--- Finalizer.delete_dependency(id, dependant, method = :finalize)

--- Finalizer.delete_all_dependency(id, dependant)

--- Finalizer.delete_by_dependant(dependant, method = :finalize)

--- Finalizer.delete_all_by_dependant(dependant)

--- Finalizer.finalize_dependency(id, dependant, method = :finalize)

--- Finalizer.finalize_all_dependency(id, dependant)

--- Finalizer.finalize_by_dependant(dependant, method = :finalize)

--- Finalizer.finalize_all_by_dependant(dependant)

--- Finalizer.finalize_all

--- Finalizer.safe
